        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Post-Brexit, needs visa now, Frankfurt agency.</p>
        <p class="text-amber-700 font-medium">△ Salary above threshold but degree recognition took 4 months (UK degree not in anabin). Had to use ZAB process. Interim used tourist visa—couldn't work, awkward start. Now sorted with TK public insurance. Lesson: start degree recognition early.</p>
