        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Hospital position, nursing degree.</p>
        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">✓ Healthcare is shortage occupation—€41,042 threshold applies. Required professional recognition (Anerkennung) for nursing credential plus language certification. Process took 8 months total but now has Blue Card with clear PR pathway.</p>
