        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Creative agency, design degree.</p>
        <p class="text-red-700 font-medium">✗ Salary below both thresholds (€45,300 general, €41,042 shortage). Design isn't a shortage occupation. Had to negotiate higher salary or consider regular work visa (§18b) instead of Blue Card. Ended up with §18b—no fast PR track, but at least working in Germany.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

